node.text:
CSF Classic: The origin story of how my civic turned into the infamous Lambo...

The "Lambo" gets a dash of flair when Linus actually lets us paint it neon pink...

node.title: I can't believe they painted my car.....

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Linus Tech Tips on July 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'GPUs should be cheaper'.
